*acroread-9.5.5-r1 (22 Oct 2014)

  22 Oct 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +acroread-9.5.5-r1.ebuild:
  revbump to fix some gx86-multilib deps and clean up the *DEPEND a little

  18 Jun 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> acroread-9.5.5.ebuild:
  Update dependencies to require guaranteed EAPI=5 or multilib ebuilds, bug
  #513718.

  15 Jun 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> acroread-9.5.5.ebuild:
  Disallow mixing of emul-linux-x86 with multilib dependencies, since all
  dependencies are unmasked now.

  27 May 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> acroread-9.5.5.ebuild:
  Support fulfilling the dependencies using multilib packages, bug #490156.

